stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ReceiveLBA
    ReceiveLBA: receive logical LBA
    ReceiveLBA --> Translate: FTLTranslator.translate(lba)
    Translate: map LBA -> (block, page)
    Translate --> BadBlockCheck

    state BadBlockCheck <<choice>>
    BadBlockCheck --> Remap: block marked bad
    BadBlockCheck --> FetchPage: block OK

    Remap: consult remap table
    Remap --> FetchPage: substitute physical (block', page)

    FetchPage: backing.read(page_addr)
    FetchPage --> ECCDecode
    ECCDecode: ECCDataLayer corrects bit errors
    ECCDecode --> ReturnBytes
    ReturnBytes: corrected bytes to caller
    ReturnBytes --> [*]
